docstring.long_description: Deletes from both x and y axes.
docstring.short_description: Returns an OrderedPair with elements deleted from requested indices.

parameters.name: default
parameters.description: The input OrderedPair to delete from

parameters.name: indices
parameters.description: specified indices to delete value(s) at from the input OrderedPair

parameters.name: length
parameters.description: number of elements to delete from the input OrderedPair, default is 1 (this only applies when one index is specified for indices parameter)

returns.description: The new OrderedPair with element(s) deleted from the input OrderedPair
